text: Yonas Malede () is an Israeli footballer who plays as a striker for Israeli Premier League club Maccabi Netanya.https://us.soccerway.com/players/yonas- malede/513736/ ==Early life== Malede was born in Kiryat Bialik, Israel, to an Ethiopian-Jewish family. ==Career== A Maccabi Netanya youth product, Malede was promoted to its senior team in 2018. ==References== ==External links== *IFA Profile Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Israeli footballers Category:Israeli Jews Category:Jewish footballers Category:Maccabi Netanya F.C. players Category:Israeli Premier League players Category:Football players from Kiryat Bialik Category:Israeli people of Ethiopian-Jewish descent Category:Association football forwards
